{"tid":311364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］死厹半夜三更自拍比有夫之婦","createTime":"2017-07-06T14:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T13:26:08.000Z","uid":31184,"like":14,"dislike":201,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31df552c38b41b3818c2608499da9d0c41e14075","tid":311364,"uid":31184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:19:56.000Z","msg":"幫朋友開post<br />\n去圖先<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/06/220112_fd7f937302c2d30b21914500b4b77273.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F06%2F220112_fd7f937302c2d30b21914500b4b77273.jpg&h=2a860634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事由呢條友係半夜三更無緣無故發張咁嘅相比我朋友老婆 <br />\n我心諗你踢撚完波好攰關佢老婆乜撚野事先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當晚就激撚到我朋友走左出去 依家連屋企都唔撚想返 <br />\n事後就用左幾個電話號碼打比佢問咩料啦 佢又夠膽死接喎 但係就唔撚出聲算係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打多幾打就封左我朋友電話號碼 <br />\n依家就希望各位巴打一齊谷爆佢電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問佢係咪想玩人妻谷上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪撚再比呢啲死狗公再出黎獻世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d3609689340822a49cec3c0a27496fc8d67768","tid":311364,"uid":23815,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:22:57.000Z","msg":"佢應該都肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 叫佢老婆氹佢講埋地址先啦"},{"pid":"ebf7cb7efab6cc78eac7f679e4966396b17d728a","tid":311364,"uid":1833,"like":55,"dislike":2,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:24:02.000Z","msg